13:["$","$L14",null,{"slug":"local-seo","locale":"en","content":{"metaTitle":"Local SEO Pricing | Transparent Plans | KINEXIS Digital","metaDescription":"Transparent local seo pricing with clear tiers and deliverables. No hidden fees. No vague retainers.","hero":{"label":"Local SEO Pricing","line1":"Local SEO Pricing","line2":"without the guesswork.","subtitle":"Fixed scope at each tier. You see what is included before you sign anything."},"answerBlock":"Map pack visibility is a business outcome, not a vanity metric. When your GMB listing ranks in the top three for service searches in your city, you get calls. When it doesn't, your competitors do. Most local businesses are losing those calls because of fixable problems: inconsistent NAP data, under-optimized GBP profiles, and service area pages that search engines can't parse. Pricing covers strategy and optimization. One-time citation cleanup is quoted based on current status.","tiers":[{"name":"Starter","range":"$$1,500/mo","description":"Single-location local SEO for service businesses in mid-competition markets.","bestFor":"Single-location local SEO for service businesses in mid-competition markets."},{"name":"Growth","range":"$$3,000/mo","description":"Multi-location or competitive market local SEO with full citation and content management.","bestFor":"Multi-location or competitive market local SEO with full citation and content management."},{"name":"Scale","range":"$$5,000+/mo","description":"Franchise or high-competition local SEO across multiple cities and service categories.","bestFor":"Franchise or high-competition local SEO across multiple cities and service categories."}],"tiersSection":{"title":"Investment guidance","subtitle":"Pricing based on market size and number of locations.","note":"Pricing covers strategy and optimization. One-time citation cleanup is quoted based on current status."},"included":["Google Business Profile Optimization","Citation Audit & Cleanup","Location Page Creation","Review Generation Strategy","Competitor Gap Analysis","Weekly Rank Tracking"],"includedSection":{"title":"What's included","subtitle":"Everything you need to dominate local search in your market.","items":[{"title":"Google Business Profile Optimization","description":"Categories, services, photos, posts, and Q&A optimized for searches that drive calls in your market."},{"title":"Citation Audit & Cleanup","description":"Consistent NAP data across 45+ directories so Google trusts your location signals."},{"title":"Location Page Creation","description":"Service area pages with real market context, not keyword-stuffed city-name templates."},{"title":"Review Generation Strategy","description":"A sustainable process for earning genuine reviews that improve map pack position and conversion rate."},{"title":"Competitor Gap Analysis","description":"We identify exactly what your top local competitors are doing better and build a plan to overtake them."},{"title":"Weekly Rank Tracking","description":"Map pack and organic position tracking for your priority local keywords, reported weekly."}]},"comparison":{"title":"Investment guidance","subtitle":"Pricing based on market size and number of locations.","layout":"progression","columns":[{"header":"Starter","highlight":false},{"header":"Growth","highlight":true},{"header":"Scale","highlight":false}],"rows":[{"label":"Google Business Profile Optimization","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Citation Audit & Cleanup","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Location Page Creation","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Review Generation Strategy","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Best for","values":["Single-location local SEO for service businesses in mid-competition markets.","Multi-location or competitive market local SEO with full citation and content management.","Franchise or high-competition local SEO across multiple cities and service categories."]},{"label":"Starting investment","values":["$$1,500/mo","$$3,000/mo","$$5,000+/mo"]}]},"faqs":[{"question":"Is there a setup fee?","answer":"Most engagements include onboarding and strategy in month one. We quote it upfront. No surprise charges on the first invoice."},{"question":"Do you require a long-term contract?","answer":"No. Month to month. Results should earn your business, not a contract clause."},{"question":"What affects my price?","answer":"Pricing covers strategy and optimization. One-time citation cleanup is quoted based on current status."},{"question":"Can I start with a smaller plan and upgrade?","answer":"Yes. Many clients start on Starter and move up once momentum builds. We plan the upgrade path so you are not rebuilding from scratch."},{"question":"How is local SEO different from regular SEO?","answer":"Regular SEO chases rankings on standard search results. Local SEO is built for the map pack: Google Business Profile, citations, reviews, and location pages. If your customers search by city or \"near me,\" you need both, but local is what puts you on the map."},{"question":"How much does local SEO cost?","answer":"Single-location businesses usually run $2,000 to $5,000 per month. Multi-location brands scale from $3,500 to $10,000+ based on how many markets you cover and how tight the competition is. We quote after looking at your locations and current visibility."},{"question":"How many Google reviews do I need?","answer":"There is no magic number. In competitive markets, staying in the top three map spots often means 50 to 100+ reviews. We focus on steady monthly volume and thoughtful responses, not a one-time push that fades."},{"question":"Can you manage multiple Google Business Profiles?","answer":"Yes. We run multi-location accounts with separate content, review workflows, and reporting per market. Franchises and multi-branch operators are a big part of what we do."}],"ctaHeadline":"Want a quote for local seo?","ctaSubtitle":"Tell us your goals, market, and scope.|We will recommend the right tier and show you what the first 90 days look like.","ctaLabel":"Get Local SEO Pricing"},"serviceHref":"/services/local-seo","serviceLabel":"Local SEO Services","breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Home","url":"/"},{"name":"Services","url":"/services"},{"name":"Local SEO Services","url":"/services/local-seo"},{"name":"Local SEO Pricing"}]}]
